#   - Kings Bay Plowshares 7 (April 4, 2018) — anti-nuclear action at Trident
#     submarine base; 6 of 7 (Liz McAlister already in DB)
#   - Resistance Conspiracy Case (May 12, 1988 arrests) — 1983-85 Armed
#     Resistance Unit bombings of US Capitol, Fort McNair, Washington Navy
#     Yard, plus NYC sites
#   - Ohio 7 / United Freedom Front (Nov 4, 1984 arrest) — anti-imperialist
#     bombings of military and corporate targets 1976-84
